{"tid":1309823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"David Webb轟1/3回報落基金經理袋　呼籲廢除MPF","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T03:46:41.000Z","uid":66811,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28a4ccb3efeb3220752203c1076baf8b3eeb14e9","tid":1309823,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:19:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2387865/David%20Webb%E8%BD%9F1-3%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B1%E8%90%BD%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E8%A2%8B%E3%80%80%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4MPF?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2387865%2FDavid%2520Webb%25E8%25BD%259F1-3%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25A2%258B%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E9%2599%25A4MPF%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=a643a8d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2387865/David%20Webb%E8%BD%9F1-3%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B1%E8%90%BD%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E8%A2%8B%E3%80%80%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4MPF?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n有「股壇長毛」之稱的David Webb，在其個人網站Webb-site發表評論，炮轟強積金收費高，回報被基金經理蠶食，是「強迫支付費用」基金，呼籲應取消強積金制度。<br />\n<br />\n他又大力炮轟強積金的收費制度，直指支付予強積金公司的費用，為投資ETF盈富基金（02800）的10倍。他指MPF是對自由市場的入侵，應該廢除。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb同時附上一篇6月27日《彭博》的報道，報道指滙豐是香港最大的強積金受託人，可謂是其中一間較低收取費用的強積金公司。可是滙豐強積金中追蹤恒生指數的基金，收費佔資產規模的0.8%，較同樣追蹤恒生指數的ETF盈富基金費用為高，盈富基金的費用僅為0.09%。<br />\n<br />\n根據積金局《強積金計劃統計摘要》，截至2019年3月31日，強積金淨資產值約為8,930億港元，自2000年強積金制度實施以來，年率化回報為4%，最新整體平均開支比率為1.52%。"},{"pid":"8d7a39c91c608f729bed0cc97a7a65a37e55e9fd","tid":1309823,"uid":25409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5b3a1c4dfaf894c923e44d00ad10ab6795feb3b","tid":1309823,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"新戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}